venue.name: The Center for Community, Culture and Change

item.description: Join us as Isabeau Esby, an internationally known psychic medium, and Dr. Joel Glenn Wixson, clinical psychologist, speak on the topic of inspiration. What causes it, where does it come from and how can we grab on to more of it. While Isabeau brings to the table an understanding that stems from spiritual experience and visionary living, Joel brings to the table a viewpoint of inspiration that was developed through the witnessing of countless, amazing life stories. A question and answer session will follow. www.IsabeauEsby.com

item.name: Psychic and Psychological Perspectives on Inspiration
